Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=26}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:21.83,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{I cried as much as I wanted.\NI've whined enough, too. - OG}{I've cried my heart out.\NI've whined enough, too. - Gaijin}I've cried my heart out.\NAnd I've whined more than enough.{Gaijin+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:25.46,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{And I'm resolved as well! - OG}{I've made my decision! - Gaijin}My mind is made up!{Viz}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:30.97,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,I have to go. Everyone's fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.35,0:00:35.35,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Please... come back to life! - OG}{Please... wake up already! - Polly}Come on! Live, dammit!{Z+Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:42.94,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Come back to life quick!\NOr it'll be too late! - OG}Hurry and wake up\Nbefore it's too late!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:46.65,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Your friends are... Your friends are...! - OG}Your friends... Your friends are...!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:57.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I thought that they had a chance\Nin this fight. Was it just a dream...? - OG}{I thought that they had a\Nchance. Was it just a dream? - Gaijin}I thought for sure they had a chance\Nagainst him... How could this happen?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:01.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What did that damn shark do? - OG}What did that damn shark just do?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:02.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:07.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{As soon as he shot water,\Nthey both vomited blood and flew... - OG}{He just sprayed them with water, but\Nthey went flying, coughing up blood. - Gaijin}{He just sprayed them with water,\Nand now they're coughing up blood! - Polly}{\q2}I thought he just sprayed them with water,\Nbut now they're coughing up blood!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:11.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I can kill humans like you without - OG}{With just a few drops of water, - Polly}All I need is a few drops of water,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:16.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{even directly touching\Nyou if I have some water. - OG}{so much as touching you,\Nif I have some water. - Gaijin}{I can kill humans like you\Nwithout even touching them. - Polly}and I can kill you lowly humans\Nwithout even touching you.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:19.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's the difference between\Nfishmen and humans. - OG}That's what separates our races.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:20.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:29.24,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{This isn't funny... - OG}This is no joke...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:35.07,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just a water shooting game to him\Nis like a shotgun shot to us... - OG}{Playing with a water gun for him is\Nlike getting hit with a shotgun for us. - Gaijin}{Playing around with water for him is\Nlike getting hit with a shotgun for us. - Polly}A splash of water from him\Nfeels like getting hit with a shotgun!{Polly - The original JP is basically like he's playing around with water, like how you'd splash your friends in the pool, but for ordinary humans like them, it's like getting their shit punched in. It's not specifically about a "water gun" or "water shooting game". A water gun is probably too anachronistic to use so...}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:37.20,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{So this is the power of a shark... - OG}I can't believe a shark\Nhas this much power...{Polly+CK}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:40.29,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{And he's in a class by\Nhimself among fishmen... - OG}Even among fishmen,\Nhe's in a league of his own...{Polly+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.59,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's in another league. - OG}He's on another level...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:47.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Die already. - OG}Just die already.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:52.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Your lives are not worth that much. - OG}{Your lives are worthless.\NNothing will be lost. - CK}{Your lives are worthless.\NAfter all, you're humans. - Polly}Nothing of value was lost.\NAfter all, your lives are meaningless.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:53.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Big Sis Nami!\N– Big Sis Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:57.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:59.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{– Nacchan...\N– Nacchan... - OG}– Nami...\N– It's Nami...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:04.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Nami! I was about to\Ncrush some pirates just now. - OG}{Hey, Nami! I was just about\Nto crush these two-bit pirates. - Gaijin}Yo, Nami! I was just about\Nto crush these two-bit pirates.{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:07.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What did you come here for? - OG}Why'd you come here?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:14.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,To kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,To kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:11.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:17.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You never learn, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:22.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}How many times did you try to kill me\Nduring the eight years you were with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:27.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You tried assassination,\Npoison, sneak attacks... - OG}{You tried assassination,\Npoison, ambushes... - Gaijin}You tried assassination,\Npoison, even ambushes...{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Were you able to actually kill me? - OG}but I'm still here.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:36.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You must be completely aware\Nthat you mere humans can't kill me. - OG}{You should've learned that mere\Nhumans like you can never kill me. - Gaijin}You should know by now that mere\Nhumans like you can never kill me.{Polly}{It should have gotten through to you\Nby now that mere humans can never kill me. - Polly+Nikki - Nikki: The "emotional acceptance" in addition to the logical one is important to me}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:40.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Now, listen. I won't kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:44.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and you can't escape from me... - OG}{but you can't escape from me either. - Polly}but you'll never escape me, either.{Polly+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:51.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You'll be our surveyor forever. - OG}You'll be our cartographer forever.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:56.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But, as you know,\NI'm a good-natured man. - OG}But, as you know,\NI'm a reasonable man.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:05:01.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If possible, I want you to be our\Nsurveyor of your own free will. - OG}If possible, I want you to be our\Ncartographer of your own free will.{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:08.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:15.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll be killing everyone\Nhere except you. - OG}{I intend to kill everyone\Nhere except you. - Gaijin}I intend to kill everyone\Nhere except for you.{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:21.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But if you happily come\Nback to the Arlong Pirates - OG}{If you're willing to come\Nback to the Arlong Pirates - Gaijin}However, if you willingly come\Nback to the Arlong Pirates{Polly+CK}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:24.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and draw sea charts\Nas one of the leaders, - OG}and draw sea charts\Nas one of our officers,{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:30.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I don't mind letting those people\Nfrom Cocoyashi Village live. - OG}{I could be convinced\Nto spare these villagers. - LP+Polly}I could be convinced to spare\Nthe people of Cocoyashi Village.{LP+Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:35.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But I can't let these guys live. - OG}{These guys are finished, though. - Gaijin}Not these two, though.{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:38.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The question is who you'll be with. - OG}{The question is who you'll side with. - Gaijin}The question is,\Nwho will you side with?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:45.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You either take my side now and\Nget saved along with the villagers, - OG}{You either join me now\Nand be spared along with the villagers, - Gaijin}{\q2}Will you join me while you still can\Nand be spared along with the villagers?{Nikki+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:50.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{or be on these weaklings' side and\Ntry fighting against me with everyone. - OG}{or team up with these weaklings\Nand try fighting me together. - Gaijin}Or will you join these weaklings\Nand try fighting me together?{Gaijin+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:55.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But with these guys you\Ndepend on in this shape, - OG}{If you depend on these\Nguys in the shape they're in, - Gaijin}{Though... if you put your money\Non guys in this kind of shape, - Polly}{\q2}Though... with the people\Nyou're betting on in this kind of shape,{Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:58.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{it's obvious that it'll be\Na tragedy for you. - OG}{it'll clearly end in tragedy for you. - Gaijin}{there's no way this doesn't\Nend in tragedy for you. - Polly}there's no way this story\Nof yours has a happy ending.{Polly+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:06.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are you my friend? - OG}{are you a member of my crew? - Gaijin}Are you with {\i1}me{\i0}?{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{their friend? - OG}are you with {\i1}them{\i0}?{Polly}{are you against me? - Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.56,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Not fair... - OG}{How unfair! - Gaijin}This isn't fair...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:17.27,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{If I say I'm friends with\NLuffy and the others, - OG}{If I say I'm part of Luffy's crew... - Polly}If I say I'm on Luffy's side...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.77,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{everyone will get killed. - OG}{everyone will be killed. - Polly}he'll kill everyone.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:21.28,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{And if I say I'm Arlong's friend, - OG}{And if I say I'm on Arlong's crew, - Gaijin}{And if I say I'm\Npart of Arlong's crew... - Polly}But if I say I'm on Arlong's side...{Z+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:23.45,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{then everyone from the\Nvillage will be saved. - OG}everyone from the\Nvillage will be saved.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:26.45,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{With my words, everyone will be... - OG}{It all depends on my decision! - Gaijin}{Everything hinges on my decision! - Polly}Everything hinges on what I say next!{Polly+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:30.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's despicable! - OG}How despicable!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:33.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No matter what she chooses,\Nhe's not going to give Nami freedom! - OG}{No matter what she chooses,\Nhe's going to keep Nami in chains! - Gaijin}{He's going to keep Nami in chains\Nno matter what she does! - Polly}Either choice keeps Nami in chains!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:36.67,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{But! - OG}Still!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.34,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy...{AP05 @27:24; AP06 @03:45}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.05,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0, 450)}Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:48.10,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:55.06,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{I must not doubt his words! - OG}{I must not doubt him! - Gaijin}I have to believe in him!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:00.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everyone, I'm sorry! - OG}Guys, I'm sorry!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:03.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Please die with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– All right!\N– All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We'll go for it! - OG}Let's do this!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We'll fight! - OG}{Let's put up a fight! - Z}Let's give 'em what for!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I see... - OG}So that's how it is...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:18.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everyone wants to be killed... - OG}{Everyone wants to die. - Gaijin}{All of you want to die. - Polly}I guess you all want to die.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:27.84,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,P-Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:32.31,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Live! Live! Live! Live! Live!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:42.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:47.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Finally...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All we have to do now is\Nremove his leg weight... - OG}All that's left is to free his legs...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:55.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So that's what you meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Big Bro Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:07:59.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:03.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Come back to life! - OG}{Come to your senses! - Gaijin}Come back to us!{Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:16.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Thirty seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:18.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I won't last longer than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:22.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That'll be enough! - OG}That'll be plenty!{Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:29.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There isn't a fountain over there. - OG}There shouldn't be\Na fountain over there...{Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:31.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Could it be that rubber man?! - OG}Is it that rubber pest?{Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about it. - OG}Don't worry about that.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, you damn half-fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:46.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I warned you not to\Nsay those words ever again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:48.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{dying Zoro! - OG}{dead man! - Gaijin}You're a dead man walking, Zoro!{Polly - he says Zoro's name out loud here; the manga also just cuts it and says "dead man" which I think works OK there, but I think this sounds a lot more menacing anyway}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:58.06,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{If I kick and break that\Nleg weight, he can fight. - OG}{If I can smash that block\Nwith a kick, he can fight. - Gaijin}If I can smash that block\Nwith a kick, he can go crazy.{Gaijin+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:09:01.90,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Luffy, you're the only one\Nwho can fight now! - OG}Luffy, you're the only one\Nwho can settle this now!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:09.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{In the sea, one with Devil Fruit\Npowers is supposed to lose even - OG}{Those with devil fruit powers struggle\Nto use those powers in the sea, - Gaijin}Those with devil fruit powers are\Nunable to use them in the sea,{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:13.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{the energy to struggle,\Nas well as his powers, and die. - OG}{let alone fight to survive, so\Nhe should be dead by now. - Gaijin}and without even the energy\Nto struggle, they die.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If he's still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:21.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{that means someone is\Nputting a damper on this game. - OG}{that means someone is\Ninterfering with our little game. - Gaijin}that means someone is\Nraining on our little parade.{Polly - apparently there is a water-based pun in the Japanese}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:22.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Glad you're okay! - OG}{I'm glad you're okay! - Gaijin}I thought we lost you!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:25.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! Oh? - OG}Yeah! Huh?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:27.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?! What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:30.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Pops, what did you do\Nwith your pinwheel? - OG}{What happened to your pinwheel? - Polly}Where did your pinwheel go?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That was a cool one. - OG}It was so cool.{Gaijin}{It was so stylish. - Polly+Nikki - apparently he says something more like "stylish", but "cool" would work just fine too lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Who cares about that right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:36.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Putting a damper? - OG}{Interfering? - Gaijin}Raining on our parade?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:39.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It didn't seem like a fair\Ngame from the start. - OG}This game of yours was\Nrigged from the start.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:44.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{At any rate, if there's a hindrance,\NI need to check on it. - OG}{At any rate, if something's getting in the\Nway, I need to check on it. - Gaijin}{At any rate, if something's in\Nthe way, I need to take a look. - Polly}At any rate, if something's getting\Nin the way, I need to check it out.{Gaijin+Z}
Comment: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,At any rate,
Comment: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{if there's a hindrance,\NI need to check on it. - OG}{if something's getting in the\Nway, I need to check on it. - Gaijin}if something's in the way,\NI need to take a look.{Polly - CPS (Gaijin is 16 CPS but I like it more)}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Out of my way. - OG}Move.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:49.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Egg Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I've got your back, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Big Bro Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Is he all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:10:00.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How brave! What a gallant arrival! - OG}{How brave! What an epic arrival! - Gaijin}How brave! What a grand entrance!{Gordy}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:03.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Fight to the full extent! - OG}{Go for broke! - Gaijin}Don't hold back!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:05.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– {\i1}That's{\i0} where you are?!\N– {\i1}That's{\i0} where you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:07.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Listen, Nami! - OG}{Can you believe it, Nami?! - Polly}Guess what, Nami!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:10.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I beat one of the leaders! - OG}{I beat one of the officers! - Gaijin}I beat one of their officers!{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:13.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{One of the leaders!\NOne of the leaders! - OG}{One of the officers! Me! I beat him! - Gaijin}One of their officers! Me! I beat him!{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:17.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, can't you somehow\Nescape on your own? - OG}{Hey, is there anything you\Ncan do to get out of this? - Gaijin}Hey, can't you get out\Nof this on your own?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh, that's impossible. - OG}{Oh, no way. - Polly}Oh, no can do.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:20.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I don't have any strength at all. - OG}{I don't have any energy at all. - Gaijin}I'm totally pooped.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:24.31,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Come out! Come out! Come out! - OG}Come on! Come on! Come on!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Big Bro Cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's\Ngoing on in the water,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:35.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{but his action must be the key! - OG}{but he must be the key! - Gaijin}but whatever he's doing\Nmust be the key!{Gaijin+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Big Bro Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:39.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Stand strong and stop Arlong! - OG}Stand firm and stop Arlong!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:42.96,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:47.08,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{We have to somehow prevent Arlong\Nfrom going into the sea, huh? - OG}We just have to stop Arlong from\Ngoing into the water somehow, huh?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.04,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,I'll stop him from moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:56.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I won't let you have your way...!{OG}{As if I'll let you do\Nwhatever you want...! - Polly}{I won't let you do\Nwhatever you want...! - Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:59.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Arlong! Look this way! - OG}{Hey, Arlong! Look here! - Gaijin}Hey, Arlong! Over here!{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:04.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wha...?! Big Bro Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:05.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:12.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Standing in my way... - OG}{Standing in my way - Gaijin}If you're standing in my way,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:11.57,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(150,150)}Rubber Band of Doom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:16.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Looks like you want to\Ndie first, Roronoa Zoro. - OG}{leads me to believe you want\Nto die first, Roronoa Zoro. - Gaijin}that must mean you want\Nto die first, Roronoa Zoro.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:18.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Now! Go, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:20.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What do you actually wanna do?! - OG}What are you trying to do?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:28.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll break your proud nose! - OG}I'll break that nose you're so proud of!{Gaijin}
Comment: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No way I'll die. - OG}{No way will I die. - Gaijin}I'll break that nose...{Gaijin}{Polly - He's not actually saying this, so maybe this is from a cut line}
Comment: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll break your proud nose! - OG}{I'll break that nose you're so proud of! - Gaijin}you're so proud of!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:36.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's a proud nose\Nbecause it's unbreakable. - OG}I'm proud of it {\i1}because{\i0}\Nit's unbreakable.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:41.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If you were at your full strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:44.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{you might've been able\Nto give it a scratch.}you might've been able to scratch it.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:02.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Ahh! That damn octopus is up! - OG}Oh, crap! That eight-legged\Nfreak is up!{Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:11.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And... what's he doing?{OG}{And... what the hell's he doing? - Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! I thought the rubber band\Nwas going to fly at me! - OG}Dammit! I thought the rubber\Nband was going to hit me!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:18.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– What?!\N– What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:21.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:26.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{See?! He was my target! - OG}See?! He was my target all along!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You were yelling "Arlong,"\Nweren't you?}You yelled, "Arlong," didn't you?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:30.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Octopus... - OG}The octopus...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:32.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:36.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I won't let you have your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:39.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll crush your friend\Nwho went into the sea! - OG}I'll crush your buddy in the water!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:51.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You don't have to be concerned\Nsince you'll all be dead, after all. - OG}No need to worry. You'll all\Nbe dead soon, after all.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:01.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Big Bro!\N– Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.85,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami-san's big sister! - OG}It's Nami's sister!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:13.44,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:18.74,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,A fishman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:22.41,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Move away, Big Sister. - OG}Get back, Nojiko!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:24.12,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll break a rock\Nlike that with my kick! - OG}{I'll break that rock with my kick! - Gaijin}I'll break that rock with one kick!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:31.04,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{That octopus! - OG}The octopus!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Octopus-Fritter Frenzy! - OG}Takoyaki Punch!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:36.38,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Big Sister! - OG}Nojiko!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So that was it? - OG}{Was that it? - Polly}Already out of steam?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That was too quick. - OG}{That was too easy. - Polly}What a disappointment.{Nikki - bit different but it captures the same sentiment}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's up with these bandages? - OG}What's under all these bandages?{Z+Polly - "excessive" was missing}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:59.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Did you fall somewhere? - OG}{Did you fall down or something? - Gaijin}Did you have a bad fall or something?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:06.45,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's this scar? - OG}What's with this wound?{Polly - with all the blood it's hard to tell it's a scar... but you can see the stitches... the word can mean either one anyway}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:23.34,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{How can he still be alive\Nwith a body like this? - OG}{How can he still be alive\Nwith wounds like this? - Gaijin}How can he still be alive\Nin this condition?{Gaijin+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.93,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,How can he still be standing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:40.32,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{What kind of eyes are they? - OG}What is that look in his eyes?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.57,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are they the eyes of\Nsomeone who's dying? - OG}{Is that the look of\Nsomeone who's dying? - Gaijin}Are these the eyes of a dying man?{Viz}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:47.83,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's a man I need to kill for sure... - OG}I definitely need\Nto take this man out...{Polly+Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:53.29,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,right here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If a person stays put, - OG}Staying still...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:05.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{their wounds won't be opened... - OG}would have kept some of\Nthe wounds from opening.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's right. - OG}That goes without saying.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You find your situation amusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:16.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:18.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm talking about the Octo-Man. - OG}I'm talking about the octofreak.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:20.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:22.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I thought I told you... - OG}Like we told you...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We win this game! - OG}{we're the winners of this game! - Polly}we win your little game!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.83,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.54,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{That scared me a bit! - OG}That scared the crap outta me!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:47.76,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're the one who made this whole\Nthing complicated in the first place! - OG}{\i1}You're{\i0} the one who complicated\Neverything in the first place!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.68,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{All right! - OG}He did it!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.18,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Go and beat up that shark bastard... - OG}{Go beat down that shark bastard... - Gaijin}{Get outta here, you asshole! - Polly}Get outta here, you blockhead!{Polly+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:57.14,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{you damn idiot! - OG}Go kick that stupid shark's ass!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Is it coming, kid? - OG}Are you free, kid?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's coming! - OG}I sure am!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:15.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Rubber boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:22.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Big Bro Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:29.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:35.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That damn rubber man...! - OG}{That damn rubber jerk...! - Gaijin}That rubber piece of trash...!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You're late, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:41.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:42.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:46.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You aren't gonna...! - OG}You wouldn't...!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:52.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let's switch places! - OG}{It's my turn! - Gaijin}My turn now!{Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– You idiot!\N– You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:01.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:03.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Whip!{!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:14.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:21.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:32.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:52.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Did you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:54.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– It's not working!\N– It's not working!{OG}{He didn't feel a thing! - Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:57.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yep. That was my warm-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:01.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That idiot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:03.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna kill him...! - OG}I'll kill him...!{Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:11.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What a bunch of scum, nobly hanging on... - OG}{It's admirable how you scum have\Nheld on by the skin of your teeth. - Gaijin}It's admirable how you lowlifes have\Nheld on by the skin of your teeth.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:16.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You'd have been happier if you\Ndied at the bottom of the sea... - OG}Though, you'd have been happier\Ndying at the bottom of the sea.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:17.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hm? Not really. - OG}Huh? Nah.{Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm happy that they saved me. - OG}I'm glad they saved me.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Can you understand my anger? - OG}{Do you understand my frustration? - Polly}{Can you understand\Nwhy I'm so furious? - Polly}Can you understand my fury?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:31.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's the anger of seeing my dear\Nbrothers crushed by worms. - OG}It's the fury of a man who has seen\Nhis dear brothers crushed by worms.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:36.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You'll realize soon enough that\Nyou should've died without fighting. - OG}{You'll soon wish that you had\Nsubmitted to your deaths. - Gaijin}You'll soon wish that you had\Nquietly submitted to your deaths.{Gaijin+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:40.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Is Big Bro Luffy gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:43.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All his fierce attacks\Nweren't effective at all... - OG}{His furious assault had\Nno effect whatsoever. - Gaijin}That crazy barrage\Ndidn't faze him at all.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:47.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,More importantly, how far\Ndid Big Bro Zoro fly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:50.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Go Luffy! I've got your back! - OG}Get him, Luffy! I've got your back!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:52.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You don't have to\Nworry about his back. - OG}{Forget about his back. - Polly}You're not helping.{Polly - This is more like the actual sentiment, the "back" thing is so weird}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:03.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If he loses, you guys will all die, too. - OG}If he loses, you're all gonna die, too.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:08.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If that happens, it's the end\Nof the East Blue, too. - OG}{If that happens, it's the end\Nfor the East Blue, as well. - Gaijin}It'll be the end of the East Blue, too.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:18.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's the terrifying difference\Nbetween you and me? - OG}{What's the bleak difference\Nbetween you and me? - Gaijin}What's the stark difference\Nbetween you and me?{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:21.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nose. - OG}Our noses.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Jaw? - OG}Our jaws?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:30.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Big Bro's joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:33.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No... He's definitely serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:34.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Webs! - OG}{Our webs! - Gaijin}The webs!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:37.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Species! - OG}It's our race!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:53.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Such a fool! He hurt\Nhimself by biting on a rock! - OG}That moron hurt himself\Nwhen he bit that rock!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now his teeth're brok... - OG}Now his teeth are crack–{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:02.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He crushed the stone pillar\Nwith his teeth! - OG}He crushed the pillar with his teeth!{Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:05.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ahh! That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:19.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Did you see... - OG}Do you see...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:23.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,the inherent power of a fishman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:28.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Heaven created you humans as\Ncreatures that bow before fishmen. - OG}{Heaven created you humans to\Nhave you bow before fishmen. - Gaijin}{\q2}Heaven created you humans\Nto prostrate yourselves before fishmen.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:32.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You humans are inferior creatures. - OG}You're inferior creatures.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:36.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We were on a different level\Nfrom the moment we were born. - OG}We're on a different level\Nfrom the moment we're born.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:52.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's true that humans can't crush\Nthat thick pillar using their teeth. - OG}It's true that humans can't crush\Na thick pillar like that with their teeth.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:55.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If that jaw gets you, it won't just give you bite marks... - OG}If that jaw gets you, it won't\Njust leave bite marks...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:03.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It'll bite clear through your bones! - OG}it'll tear clear through your bones!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:09.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:11.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:15.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{bragging over stuff like that! - OG}bragging about stuff like that!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:21.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's not like biting is the only\Nway to break stone.{OG}{I can break stone without biting it. - Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:28.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All right, Big Bro Luffy!\NYou sure told him! - OG}Nice! Score one for Big Bro Luffy!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:31.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's right!\NThe outcome is the same! - OG}{That's right! The result's the same! - Gaijin}That's right! The result is the same!{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:35.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Th-That's beside the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:38.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A stupid and weak species...\NThat's what humans are. - OG}{Humans are stupid and weak. - Gaijin}Humans are just a stupid,\Nillogical, and foolish race!{Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:42.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What can you do when you can't... - OG}{If you fall into water\Nand can't pull yourself out, - Gaijin}If you fell in the water,\Nyou couldn't even pull yourself out!{Polly+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:43.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{even pull yourself out of the water?! - OG}{then what'll you do?! - Gaijin}What {\i1}can{\i0} you do?!{Polly+Nikki}
Comment: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:43.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{even pull yourself out of the water?! - OG}then what'll you do?!{Gaijin}
Comment: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:43.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\clip(m 478.22 981.33 l 464.86 1042.67 1012.54 1077.33 1052.62 970.67)}{even pull yourself out of the water?! - OG}then what'll you do?!{Gaijin}
Comment: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:43.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\clip(m 480.89 981.33 l 467.53 1042.67 1012.54 1077.33 1052.62 970.67)}{even pull yourself out of the water?! - OG}then what'll you do?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:51.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nothing! That's why I need help! - OG}Nothing! That's why I have\Nhelp from my friends!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:58.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hm? He can also use swords? - OG}Hm? He can use swords too?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:03.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Take that... and that... and that! - OG}Take that... and that!{Polly - CPS}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:05.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:10.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It looks like you're just\Nswinging swords around. - OG}{It looks like you're just\Nswinging those blades around. - Gaijin}It looks like you're just randomly\Nswinging those blades around.{Gaijin+Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:20.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If you're just playing around,\NI'm not going to join your little game. - OG}I'm not looking\Nto play your little game.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:32.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Enough of this nonsense... - OG}I've had enough of this nonsense...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:34.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Clench your teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:22:59.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}– Wha...?! He shattered Arlong's teeth!\N– Wha...?! He shattered Arlong's teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:06.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to use\Nswords, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:10.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Huh? What's he saying that now for? - OG}Huh? What the hell\Nis he talking about?{Polly+Nikki - there isn't even a "now" in here, this is more like what he's saying}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:16.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I don't know how to sail the oceans. - OG}{I don't know how to sail. - Gaijin}I don't know how to navigate.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:19.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I can't cook...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.38,0:23:22.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I can't lie, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:23.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:27.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm confident that I\Ncan't live without help! - OG}{There's no way I can live without help! - Polly}There's no way I can\Nmake it without help!{Polly+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:34.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Fully admitting how\Npathetic you are... - OG}Fully admitting just how\Npathetic you are...{Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:37.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You sure are honest. - OG}I guess you never lie\Nthrough your teeth.{Z+Polly}{Nikki - this is a teeth pun in JP (Polly: not that we HAVE to preserve it...)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:42.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I bet your crew is\Nbothered by having... - OG}{I bet your crew is bothered\Nby having a captain... - Nikki}I pity your crew. Having an\Nincompetent captain like you...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:45.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{such an incompetent captain like you. - OG}{such an incompetent captain. - Polly}{as incompetent as you are. - Nikki}{as incompetent as you. - Nikki+Z}must be a real pain in the ass.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:51.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I wonder why your crew tried\Nso desperately to save you... - OG}I can't imagine why they'd\Ntry so desperately to save you...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.04,0:23:57.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Someone like you without any pride\Nhas the caliber to be a captain? - OG}{How can someone like you, with no\Ndamn pride, be a pirate captain? - Gaijin}{\q2}How can someone like you, without\Nan ounce of pride, be a pirate captain?{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.71,0:24:00.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What on earth can you do? - OG}{What in the world can you do? - Gaijin}What in the world can you even do?{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:02.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I can defeat you! - OG}I can beat you!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:08.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Of course, you damn idiot! - OG}{That's right, you damn idiot! - Gaijin}That's right, you idiot!{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.47,0:24:11.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If he dies, I'm gonna kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.93,0:24:14.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I've got your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.06,0:24:16.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All right, Gum-Gum! - OG}That's it, Gum-Gum!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.69,0:24:18.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Get him, Big Bro Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:24:21.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Go for it by a hair! - OG}{You've got this!\NYou're on the same level! - Gaijin}You've got this! You're on\Nthe same level by a hair!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.31,0:24:24.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Go ahead and babble,\Nyou inferior species! - OG}Go to hell, worm!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.90,0:24:28.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Ugh! He's got new teeth! - OG}Ack! He grew new teeth!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.49,0:24:32.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm a shark. New teeth\Ngrow one after another. - OG}I'm a shark. New teeth\Ngrow in one after another.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.49,0:24:36.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And they're stronger\Nthan the previous ones. - OG}{And they're sturdier\Nthan the previous ones. - Gaijin}And they're sturdier\Nthan the previous set.{Gaijin+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.79,0:24:40.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{As many times as needed... - OG}{Over and over! - dan}Each and every time!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.80,0:24:46.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.38,0:24:48.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{As many times... - OG}As many times as I want!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.47,0:24:59.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is a distinctive quality\Nthat heaven gave us. - OG}{The heavens have\Nbestowed this trait to us. - Gaijin}The heavens have\Nbestowed this trait upon us.{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.06,0:25:02.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Amazing! - OG}That's amazing!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.31,0:25:08.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are you starting to realize what a\Nsuperior species the fishmen are? - OG}{Are you starting to realize what\Na superior race the fishmen are? - Gaijin}Are you starting to realize just how\Nsuperior a race the fishmen are?{Nikki}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.70,0:25:15.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Tooth Attack! - OG}Tooth and Gum!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.33,0:25:16.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.46,0:25:22.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.05,0:25:33.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Big Bro Luffy!\N– Big Bro Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.48,0:25:44.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A-Arlong{-san}...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.40,0:25:46.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.61,0:25:48.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wha...?! B-Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.49,0:25:51.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Phew...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.24,0:25:54.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You damn rubber man! - OG}{You rubber punk! - Gaijin}You damn rubber punk!{Gaijin+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.16,0:25:59.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How dare you use my\Nbrother as a shield?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.33,0:26:01.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What're you saying? - OG}What're you talking about?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.96,0:26:03.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're the one who attacked me. - OG}You're the one who attacked.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.92,0:26:06.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Phew... Was I scared... - OG}Phew... That sure was scary.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.17,0:26:13.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.43,0:26:15.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{you damn rubber man! - OG}you rubber bastard!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.01,0:26:17.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.64,0:26:19.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I've got an interesting idea. - OG}I've got a fun idea.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.27,0:26:20.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{An interesting idea? - OG}A fun idea?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.56,0:26:23.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What in the world will he...? - OG}What in the world is he gonna do?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.77,0:26:25.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Did he come up with a secret scheme or something? - OG}Does he have some\Ntrick up his sleeve?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.23,0:26:29.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Tooth Attack! - OG}Tooth and Gum!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.22,0:26:54.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.80,0:26:57.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You... - OG}{Idiot... - Gaijin}Fool...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.26,0:27:02.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's no point in crushing\Nmy teeth repeatedly... - OG}{It's useless for you to\Nkeep destroying my teeth. - Gaijin}Crush my teeth all you want...{CEP}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.64,0:27:05.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You still don't get it?! - OG}It won't make any difference!{Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.02,0:27:08.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{B-Big Bro Luffy... - OG}B-Big Bro Luffy,{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.77,0:27:11.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You surely don't mean\Nyour interesting idea is... - OG}surely you didn't mean\Nthat this is your fun idea...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.23,0:27:14.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Look! I've got fangs, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.20,0:27:22.75,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{S-So there wasn't\Nany secret scheme? - OG}{\q2}– S-So he didn't have a trick up his sleeve?\N– S-So he didn't have a trick up his sleeve?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.62,0:27:28.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How long are you going to... - OG}How long are you going to keep...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.04,0:27:31.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{keep fooling around?! - OG}fooling around?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.84,0:27:36.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I got bitten by a shark! - OG}{The shark bit me! - Gaijin}Shark attack! I've been bit!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.39,0:27:39.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}– That's because you're playing around!\N– That's because you're playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.35,0:27:42.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's not like I'm playing around. - OG}I'm not trying to mess around.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.81,0:27:44.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Tooth Attack! - OG}Tooth and Gum!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.50,0:28:09.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{– He got bit!\N– He got bit! - OG}– Arlong bit him!\N– Arlong bit him!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.72,0:28:20.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How do you like your own teeth?! - OG}How do you like that?\NA tooth for a tooth!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.18,0:28:24.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Even if it's my teeth\Nthat you used, - OG}You can use my teeth all you want.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.93,0:28:28.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{it's your weak jaw after all. - OG}You're still stuck with that weak jaw.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.15,0:28:29.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.65,0:28:35.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Shark teeth become\Nuseful when they come - OG}{A shark's teeth are only\Nas good as his jaws, - Gaijin}A shark's bite can only rip through\Nflesh thanks to its powerful jaw!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.78,0:28:37.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{with a strong jaw that\Ncan bite off the meat! - OG}{which tear through flesh! - Gaijin}{which can tear through flesh! - Polly}Teeth alone won't cut it!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.91,0:28:42.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Ahh! Big Bro's arm's\Ngonna get bitten off! - OG}Ahh! Big Bro's gonna lose his arm!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.08,0:28:44.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=27}===============================DIALOGUE============================
